Package stratpoint.samuelnieva

Class Manga

java.lang.Object
stratpoint.samuelnieva.EntityLayer.Book
stratpoint.samuelnieva.EntityLayer.Manga
public class Manga extends Book
This subclass represent Manga books. The unique attributes for this subclass are the illustrator of the book, the genre and the volume of the Manga.
